snippet.title: Star Raiders II - Atari XL/XE - Longplay No Commentary
snippet.description:
Star Raiders II on the Atari 8 bit home computer is one of the very few that I can spend almost an entire hour on without stopping. Despite repetitive game play, the assortment of tasks required to complete the game keep it fun.

Thanks for watching this video.  For a review of this game, click the following link:

Star Raiders II Review: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jk4m21R3W50
